{
  "id": "RAW_81c6ba",
  "title": "大模型——重构人机交互的智能革命",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2NDU4OTExOQ==&mid=2247690852&idx=2&sn=228a94ef49d9373518d9448beca78a5e",
  "date": "2025-07-02 00:45:39",
  "author": "腾讯云开发者",
  "siteName": "腾讯云开发者",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mck97uh8jrn\" style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mck97virn0j\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">从Transformer架构的革新到千亿参数的涌现能力，大模型正以惊人的速度重塑数字世界的底层逻辑。这场技术革命中，自注意力机制破解了长序列处理的千年难题，MoE架构实现了效率与规模的黄金平衡，多模态融合让机器首次理解世界的复合语义。企业级部署呈现多重变奏。在应用战场，动态记忆网络让销售AI学会千人千面沟通，询价转化率飙升；KV-Cache缓存技术将推理速度提升5倍，也为显存占用埋下伏笔。当Temperature参数从0.1调至100，AI在严谨律师与先锋诗人之间自由切换，揭示着可控性与创造力的深层辩证。这场革命中，中文语义理解、垂直场景融合、端侧部署优化正构筑起中国特色的技术护城河。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-mpa-action-id=\"mck97uh8jrn\" style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mck97virn0j\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">本次选文作者均为一线开发大神：羚羊工业互联网股份有限公司 高级系统架构师 宋国磊、北京华医网科技股份有限公司信息技术部副总经理 蓝葛亮、蓝莺IM创始人 &amp; CEO 一乐、联想诺谛智能首席架构师 曹洪伟，现在让我们来看看大神们如何解析大模型与其应用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:block;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;pointer-events:initial;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;pointer-events: initial;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;pointer-events: initial;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-size:24px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;pointer-events:initial;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;pointer-events: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-size:24px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;pointer-events:initial;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;pointer-events: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 24px;visibility: visible;pointer-events: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;pointer-events: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-weight:bolder;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;pointer-events:initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">趋势解读篇</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;pointer-events: initial;\"><br></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">《大模型发展历程：技术演进与趋势洞察》</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">推荐语：本文纵贯 2017-2025 年大模型演进，解构 Transformer 奠基、规模化突破、多模态智能体崛起三阶段，剖析 GPT-3、Gemini Ultra 等代表模型技术突破，对比中美「基础研究 + 通用能力」与「应用落地 + 成本优化」路径，揭示智能体协作、端侧部署等未来趋势，为技术人呈现从架构创新到产业变革的全景脉络。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><a class=\"weapp_image_link js_weapp_entry\" data-miniprogram-type=\"image\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;color:rgb(87, 107, 149);text-decoration:none;-webkit-user-drag:none;cursor:default;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;display:inline-block;vertical-align:bottom;user-select:none;overflow:hidden;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;width:100%;\" data-miniprogram-appid=\"wxe633721849e57c24\" data-miniprogram-path=\"delivery/pages/webview/index?=&amp;url=https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/2529154\" data-miniprogram-nickname=\"腾讯云会员\" data-miniprogram-servicetype=\"0\" data-miniprogram-applink=\"#小程序://腾讯云会员/Und4KNG10fj0Jjm\" data-miniprogram-imageurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/VY8SELNGe94pOJPKzg8Yw0dvE7UoLDuPlZUqPskkkibSWZMDu0O3oeBvz37daHerehFofJqP08OUghia9LGicMBRA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;tp=webp\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ef8afa37-7c3b-4ed7-40c1-630ba5defd00/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2857142857142857\" data-w=\"700\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;border: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 661px !important;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ef8afa37-7c3b-4ed7-40c1-630ba5defd00/public\"></a></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mcj0aqmts2l\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">*点击图片查看全文</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:block;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;pointer-events:initial;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;pointer-events: initial;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;pointer-events: initial;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-size:24px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;pointer-events:initial;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;pointer-events: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-size:24px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;pointer-events:initial;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;pointer-events: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 24px;visibility: visible;pointer-events: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;pointer-events: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;font-weight:bolder;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;pointer-events:initial;\"><span leaf=\"\">技术原理类</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;pointer-events: initial;\"><br></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">《大模型的性能提升：KV-Cache》</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">大模型生成文字时，每步都要算前一句的关联，重复计算特费时间。KV-Cache 就像给模型备个记忆小本本，，把算过的关键数据存起来，下次直接翻本子不用重算，能让生成速度快 5 倍。本文将从理论到代码实践讲解KV-Cache，助你实现LLM的性能飞速提升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><a class=\"weapp_image_link js_weapp_entry\" data-miniprogram-type=\"image\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;color:rgb(87, 107, 149);text-decoration:none;-webkit-user-drag:none;cursor:default;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;display:inline-block;vertical-align:bottom;user-select:none;overflow:hidden;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;width:100%;\" data-miniprogram-appid=\"wxe633721849e57c24\" data-miniprogram-path=\"delivery/pages/webview/index?url=https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/2532746&amp;=\" data-miniprogram-nickname=\"腾讯云会员\" data-miniprogram-servicetype=\"0\" data-miniprogram-applink=\"#小程序://腾讯云会员/efQTlMFWEuK5d2f\" data-miniprogram-imageurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/VY8SELNGe94pOJPKzg8Yw0dvE7UoLDuPzUewrcw3803BDSgfiaemuqV1bkXf7Tia3vpc21215s7bqibFySpmLYibUw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;tp=webp\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/92743e52-fcb9-4517-f705-6b891daf7100/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2857142857142857\" data-w=\"700\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;border: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 661px !important;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/92743e52-fcb9-4517-f705-6b891daf7100/public\"></a></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mcj0aqmtz5y\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">*点击图片查看全文</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">《大模型的温度？解读Temperature》</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">在大型语言模型（LLM）生成文本的核心机制中，“温度（Temperature）”参数扮演着关键角色。它并非物理概念，而是一个精妙的数学调控因子，作用于模型输出层（通常是Softmax函数），直接影响下一个词的概率分布。并恰当运用这一参数，是在LLM应用中平衡输出可靠性与创造性潜力的核心杠杆。本文将深入剖析其原理、应用场景及潜在影响。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:n