 textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">推荐语：“在 AI 赛道上，先活下来的未必是跑得最快的，而是懂得在安全与效率间走钢丝的智者。”当 GPT-4 的算力需求堪比全球 Top500 超算总和时，企业智能化转型正站在抉择的十字路口 —— 私有化部署如同一把重剑，用千万级初期投资换取数据主权；云端服务则像灵活的匕首，按 Token 计费却暗藏数据泄露风险。这篇深度分析以 200 家企业调研为锚点，剖开 67% 大企业选择私有化的安全逻辑，解析 78% 中小企业投奔云端的成本密码。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><a class=\"weapp_image_link js_weapp_entry\" data-miniprogram-type=\"image\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;color:rgb(87, 107, 149);text-decoration:none;-webkit-user-drag:none;cursor:default;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;display:inline-block;vertical-align:bottom;user-select:none;overflow:hidden;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;width:100%;\" data-miniprogram-appid=\"wxe633721849e57c24\" data-miniprogram-path=\"delivery/pages/webview/index?url=https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/2523839&amp;=\" data-miniprogram-nickname=\"腾讯云会员\" data-miniprogram-servicetype=\"0\" data-miniprogram-applink=\"#小程序://腾讯云会员